API Gateway = Security boundary, not business logic.
ECURITY GOALS (CLEAR INTENT)

Your gateway must:

Validate JWT tokens

Allow public endpoints (auth, health)

Block everything else

Support React + Flutter CORS

Be stateless

Be reactive end-to-end

spring:
  security:
    oauth2:
      resourceserver:
        jwt:
          issuer-uri: https://issuer.example.com
Keycloak

Auth0

Cognito

Custom IdP